{\"ngram\": \"the 800-meter freestyle\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ledecky, 27, remains undefeated in the 1,500-meter freestyle in her professional career, having won five world titles and the inaugural Olympic gold medal in the event at the 2021 Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 1156, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1,500-meter freestyle\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"her professional career\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1048}, {\"ngram\": \"five world titles\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"the inaugural Olympic gold medal\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1115}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1128}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2021 Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1155}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She holds the world record in the 1,500-meter freestyle, which she has set six times, and now boasts the 20 fastest times ever recorded in this race.\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1306, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world record\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1,500-meter freestyle\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1212}, {\"ngram\": \"the 20 fastest times\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1278}, {\"ngram\": \"this race\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1305}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The last time Ledecky was beaten in the 1,500-meter freestyle, she was a high school student competing in a regional meet in the Maryland suburbs of Washington, DC, 14 years ago.\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1437, \"end\": 1445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryland_Terrapins\", \"score\": 0.5698884391646668, \"rank\": 0.6225564634591668, \"text\": \"Maryland\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryland_Terrapins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryland_Terrapins\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\":